      "content": "\u003cdiv class\u003d\"introduction img-head\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class\u003d\"header\"\u003e\n    \u003cimg src\u003d\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,\u003d\u003d\" alt\u003d\"App Icon\" /\u003e\n    \u003ch3\u003eWelcome to Similar Company Finder\u003c/h3\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOverview\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      A GenAI-powered similarity discovery tool that identifies companies similar to a given input company.\n      It does this by profiling their market position, customer base, and brand narrative, then matching and ranking similar organizations.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eInput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eCompany Name\u003c/strong\u003e : The name of the company to find similarities for.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eLead Name\u003c/strong\u003e : The name of the relevant stakeholder or contact person.\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eLead Industry\u003c/strong\u003e: The industry or sector the company operates in (e.g., Fintech, SaaS).\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eProduct Name\u003c/strong\u003e : The primary product or service offered by the company.\u003c/li\u003e\n    \u003c/ul\u003e\n  \u003c/section\u003e\n\n  \u003csection\u003e\n    \u003ch4\u003eOutput\u003c/h4\u003e\n    \u003cul\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eSimilar Companies:\u003c/strong\u003e A list of 5-10 organizations similar to the input company\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e+\u003c/span\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eSimilarity Score:\u003c/strong\u003e Numerical score indicating how closely each company matches\u003c/li\u003e\n      \u003cli